  Unmasked for x86.  

  16 Dec 2002; Daniel Ahlberg <aliz@gentoo.org> lvm-user-1.0.5.ebuild :
  Closes #12219, added filter-flags.  

  06 Dec 2002; Rodney Rees <manson@gentoo.org> : changed sparc ~sparc keywords
 
